race.comment: EAGLE VISION (10) missed the placings two runs back then improved last start but found a couple better over 1006m at this track, beaten 2.25 lengths after being prominent at the turn. Has the class to take this out. CANOGA (9) was out of the money when resuming from a spell last start over 1106m at this track, beaten 4 lengths after being in the firing line on the corner. Nicely placed to take this out. JET PACK (2) is a three-year-old filly who has just one minor placings to her name in five starts. Failed to threaten when fresh from a spell last start, beaten 6 lengths into fifth over 1106m at this track (Dirt). Can do much better. DEADLY BEAUTY (7) is yet to break through after seven starts but not far off a win. Placed two back then missed the frame but was thereabouts last time over 1106m at this track (Dirt). Can sneak into the finish. Something for the Multiples: EXPECT A PATRIOT (1)
